text:
Yeah, it's a great design!
Makes me feel like I'm back in high school!

What do you think, Producer-san?
Do I look good in it?

Haha, of course you do.
It suits you perfectly.

─ If you don't mind, could you give me a
different phrase than "it suits you"?

Hm...? If that's the case...
I'll try to feel like I'm back in high school too...

Hm, with that, Natsuha now seems like...
an admired senior to me.

Hehe, thank you...!
...So, what are you going to do?

Hm...?
What do you mean by "what are you going to do"...?

If there's something to convey, it should be said—...
Seniors graduate before juniors, after all.
